# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
#  ESTRATÉGIAS DE DESCONTO
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar estratégias
GET http://localhost:8000/api/strategies
Accept: application/json

###

### Atualizar estratégia (volume)
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/strategies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "label": "Desconto por Volume",
    "discount_rate": 0.10,
    "threshold_value": 3,
    "is_active": 1
}

###

### Atualizar estratégia (fidelidade)
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/strategies/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "label": "Desconto por Fidelidade",
    "discount_rate": 0.05,
    "threshold_value": 12,
    "is_active": 1
}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
#  CLIENTES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar clientes (paginado)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/clients?page=1&per_page=15
Accept: application/json

###

### Buscar cliente por ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/clients/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar cliente (CPF)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/clients
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Lojas King",
    "document": "99999999909",
    "email": "contato@lojasking.com",
    "status": "active"
}

###

### Criar cliente (CNPJ)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/clients
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Empresa LTDA",
    "document": "11222333000181",
    "email": "contato@empresa.com",
    "status": "active"
}

###

### Editar cliente
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/clients/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "João Silva Atualizado",
    "status": "inactive"
}

###

### Excluir cliente
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/clients/1
Accept: application/json

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
#  SERVIÇOS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar serviços (paginado)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/services?page=1&per_page=15
Accept: application/json

###

### Buscar serviço por ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/services/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar serviço
POST http://localhost:8000/api/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Suporte Técnico",
    "base_monthly_value": 350.00
}

###

### Editar serviço
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/services/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Suporte Técnico Premium",
    "base_monthly_value": 500.00
}

###

### Excluir serviço
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/services/1
Accept: application/json

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
#  CONTRATOS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar contratos (paginado — inclui itens e total mensal calculado)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/contracts?page=1&per_page=15
Accept: application/json

###

### Buscar contrato por ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/contracts/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar contrato
POST http://localhost:8000/api/contracts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "client_id": 1,
    "start_date": "2026-01-01",
    "end_date": null
}

###

### Cancelar contrato
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/contracts/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "canceled"
}

###

### Adicionar serviço ao contrato
POST http://localhost:8000/api/contracts/1/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "service_id": 1,
    "quantity": 2,
    "unit_value": 350.00
}

###

### Remover item do contrato
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/contracts/1/items/1
Accept: application/json

###
